---
title: Curried Paneer Dahl Pie with Puff Pastry Top
description: Chef Mimi has combined two of our favourite things - pies and curries - to create a delicious recipe perfect for any night of the week. Seasoned with our specially blended pasanda spice, the filling of our pie is a delicious mix of lentils, tomato purée, carrot and paneer cheese. Topped with buttery puff pastry and served with a sprinkle of spring onions, you can’t go wrong with this winning dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/curried-paneer-dahl-pie-6d88f9b0-2a67601a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/curried-paneer-dahl-pie-5f352f54b5377d472f3d84c4-9601574c.pdf
author: Mimi Morley
servings: 2
cuisine: Indian
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/curried-paneer-dahl-pie-5f352f54b5377d472f3d84c4
course: main course
time required: 40 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 1098 kcal
